== Umusaruro ==
Iyi filime yakozwe ishingiye ku bikorwa by'inyeshyamba mu majyaruguru y'uburasirazuba bwa Nijeriya yagaragayemo abakinnyi bagera ku 3.000, abakinnyi 100 hamwe n'abakozi 100 batunganya, naho aho bakorewe ni Ijebu - Miango, Agace k'ubutegetsi bwa Bassa, muri Leta ya Plateau, muri [[Nijeriya]] . Umusaruro watwaye iminsi igera kuri 50 kugirango urangire, bitwara igereranyo cya N200 kugeza kuri miliyoni 300 nkingengo yumusaruro.  

== Umugambi ==
Nyuma yo gushimutwa hamwe nabandi bakobwa 245 bo mwishuri rye, umusore mwiza Salma (Asabe Madaki), umwana wenyine wababyeyi be bafite imyaka 17 nabandi bakorewe kubana nabaterabwoba mukigo cyabo. Ibi byamuviriyemo guhungabanya inzozi ze ariko we, nubwo, uko ibintu bimeze ubu yagumye mubyukuri mubuzima bwe. Goni, umwe mu nyeshyamba, araza maze bombi bakundana bidatinze barashyingirwa. Mugihe ubuzima bugoye, hamwe no kwamburwa urupfu numubabaro, inyeshyamba nabakunzi babo bidatinze. 

